      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-zls-des    to   w-tes-cod-lst-des      .
           move      w-let-arc-zls-vlt    to   w-tes-cod-lst-vlt      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione descrizione listino         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-des-lst-000      thru vis-des-lst-999        .
