                     go to vis-per-pvg-500.
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      01                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
